flowchart TD
    A[Error Reported] --> B[Triage Severity]
    B --> C{Reproducible?}
    C -- No --> D[Request Repro Steps]
    C -- Yes --> E[Debug Guide Lookup]
    E --> F[Apply Fix]
    F --> G[Add Regression Test]
    G --> H[Write Retrospective]
    H --> I[Update Error Registry]
    I --> J[Close Incident]
